name: Sichuan Airlines A330-243 [B-6517] Dawn Landing at Vancouver Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
Here is my first plane spotting video from Vancouver International Airport, featuring a Sichuan Airlines A330 touching down on Runway 08L after a 9 hour flight from Shenyang, China. This was a completely new airline for me, so it was pretty cool to see. As you can see, I found delpillar's favorite location ;) I hope you enjoy, and stay tuned for a lot more footage to come!

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
